      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey Monday Community! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/waving_hand.png?v=14\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>We’re excited to share a powerful new update to <strong><a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=5a10b399e0bf62c3b316ba5d004b56a7&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">DocCreate</a></strong> that’s designed to make your documentation process even faster and more visual. You can now <strong>automatically embed images directly from both image and file columns</strong> in your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> boards into your DocCreate documents! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=14\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=14\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> What’s New:</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automatically capture visuals from <strong>image and file columns</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Embed them seamlessly into your docs<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Perfect for field teams, real estate, facility management, and more<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> 100% integrated with your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> workflow</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/television.png?v=14\" title=\":television:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":television:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Watch it in action:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-p6V-pN-fFE?si=yNiQ7MWwhaxsICcK\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/movie_camera.png?v=14\" title=\":movie_camera:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":movie_camera:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> See the feature demo on YouTube</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=14\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Ready to try it? Install DocCreate here:</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=14\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=5a10b399e0bf62c3b316ba5d004b56a7&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Install DocCreate on monday.com</a></p>"
